      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a well-cared-for enthusiast car. The exterior retains its original deep luster, showing only minor, superficial signs of road use consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with supple leather seating and fully functional electronics throughout. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; I have maintained a rigorous service schedule, including a recent comprehensive inspection, oil change, and brake pad replacement. It shifts smoothly, pulls strong, and handles the road with quiet confidence. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine respect, this car is ready for its next chapter.",
